Bitlove,is,a,service,for,creating,and,seeding,torrents,for,all,enclosures,of,an,RSS,or,Atom,feed,especially,podcast,feeds,The,Bitlove,API,allows,developers,to,use,the,URL,of,the,original,podcast,files,to,obtain,torrent,and,source,information,It,also,allows,developers,to,find,the,URLs,of,public,feeds,that,have,their,enclosures,mapped,to,torrents